### Frontend Components

#### [MODIFY] [admin-analytics.tsx](file:///c:/Users/PC/Fia-Cbt-main/fgsigbohocbtv1/client/src/pages/admin-analytics.tsx)
Overhaul the dashboard view to display the 5 cards with mini chart previews:
1. **Student Pass Probability Predictor Card**: Embedded horizontal progress bar. Drill-down: student list table with At-Risk score sorting.
2. **Cognitive Fatigue & Pacing Trajectory Card**: Mini line graph displaying response time vs accuracy slope. Drill-down: Scatter plots isolating Fast & Careless vs Exhausted.
3. **Exam Cheating & Integrity Audit Report Card**: Colored donut chart. Drill-down: Security Audit Center showing prioritized threat log and telemetry timeline.
4. **Class & Subject Grade Distribution Card**: Mini bell curve overlaying histogram. Drill-down: Curriculum and Cohort Distribution curve explorer.
5. **Question Item Analysis Spreadsheet Card**: Mini matrix preview of flagged questions. Drill-down: sortable Psychometric Ledger spreadsheet.

Introduce the **Unified Global Filter Bar** on all drill-down pages:
- Selection sequence: `School Term ➔ Target Class ➔ Subject`.
- Dynamic menu filtering: Choosing a Class limits available Subjects to those within the selected Class.

